---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Who I am and what this blog is about"
	pubDate={new Date('July 04 2026')}
>
	<p>
		I'm Rajeev — a software engineer working on global-scale customs and logistics platforms,
		based near Pune, India. I build distributed systems by day (.NET, Kubernetes, Azure, Kafka)
		and trading systems by night.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is a build log. I write about infrastructure that fails in interesting ways, the
		engineering behind systematic trading, and what I'm learning as AI changes how software gets
		built. Everything here is something I actually ran, broke, or fixed — no thought-leadership,
		no listicles.
	</p>

	<p>
		Posts land roughly monthly. If I got something wrong, tell me — that's the fastest way I
		learn.
	</p>
</Layout>
